    <item>
      <title>中国人民银行继续洗牌，另一位副行长被替换</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-26/pboc-shuffling-continues-with-another-deputy-governor-replaced</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国务院任命陆雷为中国人民银行副行长，这是自 7 月以来的第三位新任央行高级官员，也是本月的第二位新任高级官员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-26/pboc-shuffling-continues-with-another-deputy-governor-replaced</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Dec 2023 11:59:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰希望通过法案草案打破动员僵局</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-26/ukrainian-cabinet-submits-draft-law-to-boost-mobilization-effort</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰内阁向议会提交了一份法律草案，为军队制定了新的动员计划，这是在俄罗斯入侵进入第23个月之际解决政治和军事领导层在征兵问题上分歧的最新尝试。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-26/ukrainian-cabinet-submits-draft-law-to-boost-mobilization-effort</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Dec 2023 11:48:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
